profile: YUL will be a glittering embodiment of the ultimate in luxury urban living in the heart of downtown Montreal. The development features two “shifted block” towers rising 38 storeys high, flanked to the south by townhouses on what is currently known as Overdale Square. The centrepiece will be an enormous enclosed common area exclusively for residents, containing a huge courtyard, a fitness area, an indoor pool, and an outdoor pool that converts into a skating rink during winter. YUL. Prestige. Pride of place. Privacy.
